text: Ila anu: "O allah, visva samrajyadhipati! Nivu istapadina variki rajyadhikaranni prasadistavu mariyu nivu korina varini rajyadhikaram nundi tolagistavu mariyu nivu istapadina variki gauravanni (saktini) prasadistavu mariyu nivu korina varini parabhavam palu cestavu. Ni cetilone melunnadi. Niscayanga, nivu pratidi ceyagala samardhudavu
